fields.name: Felizeyeart Gallery
fields.location: Jl. Raya Pengosekan Kaja No.102, MAS, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571
fields.description: This collection features a carefully curated selection of small art pieces that are perfect for adding warmth and character to cozy spaces. From delicate watercolors to bold abstracts, these small paintings pack a punch and add visual interest to any room. Each piece has been created with a keen eye for detail and an understanding of the importance of creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.

fields.name: Bali Parcel
fields.location: Jl. Raya Kengetan, Singakerta, Kecamatan Ubud, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80571
fields.description: In business since 1995, Bali Parcel a professional manufacturer, exporter, supplier, and wholesaler of hand-made natural wooden carvings, decoration, ornament, figurines, furniture, as well as fashion jewelry and fashion accessories. Bali Parcel or CV Bali Parcel is based in Gianyar, Ubud, Bali Indonesia. Each hand-made souvenir is conventionally handcrafted with intricate patterns, hand carved and hand painted, and highlighting natural wood tones. Selection includes wooden carvings and sculptures of sea creature, animal, handicrafts, home & interior decor and ornaments, and furniture.

fields.name: Pithecanthropus Bali
fields.location: Jl. Subak Telaga I No.9, Ketewel, Kec. Sukawati, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80582
fields.description: Culture in the forms of everyday art is what we envisioned Pithecanthropus more than 25 years ago. Started as a small gift shop with curated collections of traditional art from various ethnic groups across Indonesian archipelago, we are committed to relentlessly rediscover Indonesian culture.
